column2: All urban - the percentage of the population in an urban area is 100%
Mostly urban - the percentage of the population in an urban area is between >=50% and <100%
Mostly rural - the percentage of the population in an urban area is between >0% and <50%
All rural - the percentage of the population in an urban area is 0%
The percentage of the population in an urban or rural area is unknown
State, county, or tract are invalid
State and tract are valid, but county was not reported
State + county + tract combination was not found
State, county, or tract are blank or unknown
